INVALID_TRANSPORT_MESSAGE.message: Unexpectedly received a message from the transport that was not an object

UNSUPPORTED_RPC_REQUEST.message: Received an RPC request that was not an puffs_subscription

NO_SUBSCRIPTION_ID.message: Received an puffs_subscription request without a subscription id

NO_SUBSCRIPTION_RESULT.message: Received an puffs_subscription request without a result

INVALID_MESSAGE_ID.message: Received a message from the blockchain that did not have a valid id

JSON_RPC_REQUEST_NOT_FOUND.message: Unable to locate original request for blockchain response

INVALID_BLOCK.message: Block data expected, but received null or malformed block. Is your PUFFScoin node available and responding?

BLOCK_NOT_FOUND.message: Block not found when attempting to retrieve block data from PUFFScoin Node. This node may be unavailable our out of sync.

NULL_CALL_RETURN.message: Expected contract call to return value, received null

NULL_TRANSACTION_HASH.message: Expected transaction hash from PUFFScoin node, received null

TRANSACTION_RETRY_MAX_EXCEEDED.message: Maximum number of transaction retry attempts exceeded

TRANSACTION_NOT_CONFIRMED.message: Polled network but could not confirm transaction
